{"title":"一分钟不能忘记","authors":["绿原"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":12,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一分钟不能忘记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一分钟不能忘记："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人和朝鲜人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都喝鸭绿江的水……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一根割不断的血管"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连着中国和朝鲜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一分钟不能忘记："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝鲜在硝烟中  在乌云下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揪着美国杀人犯在搏斗——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能让这群人头兽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝朝鲜的血！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啃朝鲜的骨头！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热的血，烫烂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它的肺腑！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硬骨头，割断"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它的咽喉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一分钟不能忘记："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年日本人侵占了朝鲜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，从朝鲜——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着中国一步步逼来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抢过我们  打过我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砍过我们  剁过我们！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一分钟不能忘记："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，美国人  翻印了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日本人的旧棋谱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一着一着：向朝鲜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向我们的东北！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向我们的山海关！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向全中国！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一分钟不能忘记呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（已经站起来了的中国人民！）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝鲜的大火在西北燃烧……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的土地灼热了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从朝鲜向全世界括过去的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这场疯狂的侵略的大火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"需要我们负责去灭掉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"援助朝鲜呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"援助朝鲜呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一分钟不能忘记："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的人民！）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"援助朝鲜就是——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫我们的祖国。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}